1. *Razumeti* ću šta mi treba da uradim. (I will understand what I need to do.)
2. On je *razumeo* moju želju. (He understood my wish.)
3. Ona je *razumela* da je nešto pogrešno. (She realized that something was wrong.)
4. On je *razumeo* da je to pogrešno. (He understood that it was wrong.)
5. Ona je *razumela* koliko je to važno. (She understood how important it was.)
6. On je *razumeo* šta se desilo. (He understood what had happened.)
7. Oni su *razumeli* da moraju da učine više. (They understood that they had to do more.)
8. Mi smo *razumeli* da je to njihova poslednja šansa. (We realized that this was their last chance.)